                                       → 500 ⚠  (when channel gone — SIM balance)

=== Known Issues ===
1. SIM balance — inter-SIM calls fail quickly (PJSIP goes Down -> Local chans
   cleaned up before hangup attempts). Hangup returns 500/"No active channel".
2. simcards table empty — PUT alias/phone endpoints return 404.
3. SMS body — inbound SMS with empty message body (known carrier behavior).
4. POST /contacts requires client-generated UUID id — unusual but by design.
5. GET /sms requires ?page — no default assumed.

